Token.Abstract: Get Active Mode of the device.

Parameter.Name: isTemp
Parameter.Abstract: True value specifies the changes are temporary overwrides for settings. The changes are not saved into the EEPROM and take immediate effect (no rebooting required). False value specifies the changes are permanently overwrides for settings And also saved into the EEPROM. The changes will keep after rebooting the device. Please make sure the setting of frequency is conform to standards.
